name: The Lone Raver Glitch #0.1
description: Created in collaboration with Coventry (UK) based digital artist Sean Graham and visual artist Sherrie Edgar, The Lone Raver expresses the importance of club culture and dancing during a period of social separation.  The image has been processed through a text editor and embedded with the artists crypto-wallet ID in response to an exploration into the emergence of (Clean) NFT’s and their disruptive nature, in turn creating a glitch of the original render.  Edition 1/1  1920 × 1080 - BMP  Instagram - @Sean.Graham.Digital Instagram - @sherriegram
